  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Bible Adventures is an unlicensed religious game released for the Nintendo Entertainment System in 1990. It was developed and published by Wisdom Tree in 1990. It was later ported to the Sega Mega Drive in 1995.\nIn this Single or Multiplayer game, there are three different stories that can played throughout, including Baby Moses, Noah's Ark and David and Goliath, all being from the Old Testament of the Bible. The game has a gameplay style similar to Super Mario Bros. 2.",
